sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Vue as Vue Frontend
    participant Discord as Discord OAuth
    participant Backend as Spring Boot
    participant JWT as JwtUtil (RSA)

    User->>Vue: Click "Login with Discord"
    Vue->>Discord: Redirect to OAuth URL
    User->>Discord: Authorize Application
    Discord-->>Vue: Callback with Auth Code
    Vue->>Backend: POST /api/auth/discord/callback
    Note over Vue,Backend: {code, redirectUri}
    Backend->>Discord: Exchange Code for Token
    Discord-->>Backend: Access Token + Refresh Token
    Backend->>Discord: GET /users/@me
    Discord-->>Backend: User Info (id, username, avatar)
    Backend->>Backend: Create/Update User in DB
    Backend->>JWT: Generate RSA-signed JWT
    JWT-->>Backend: JWT Token
    Backend-->>Vue: Return JWT Token

    Note over Vue: Store JWT in localStorage

    Vue->>Backend: GET /api/guilds (Bearer JWT)
    Backend->>JWT: Validate JWT Signature
    JWT-->>Backend: User Claims
    Backend-->>Vue: Guild List
